Mrs Hogwallop up and R-U-N-N-O-F-T.

143
00:10:49,201 --> 00:10:52,204
She must have been lookin' for answers.

144
00:10:52,538 --> 00:10:55,708
Possibly. Good riddance,
as far as I'm concerned.

145
00:10:55,958 --> 00:10:58,878
I do miss her cooking, though.

146
00:10:59,045 --> 00:11:02,965
- This stew's awful good.
- Think so?

147
00:11:03,215 --> 00:11:05,885
I slaughtered this horse last Tuesday.

148
00:11:06,093 --> 00:11:10,723
I'm afraid she's startin' to turn.

