Hold up!
Ain't you ever heard of negotiatin'?

197
00:13:37,286 --> 00:13:39,538
We could talk this thing out.
I hate fire!

198
00:13:39,872 --> 00:13:44,543
You lousy, yella-bellied...
Pete, we need one voice.

199
00:13:44,877 --> 00:13:48,381
Careful with that fire!

200
00:13:49,131 --> 00:13:51,050
Light the loft, son.

201
00:13:51,217 --> 00:13:53,552
Aah! I hate fire!

202
00:13:53,719 --> 00:13:57,890
Gapped-toothed, carpetbaggin',
motherless spawn of hell!

203
00:13:58,140 --> 00:14:00,893
Step back. Damn it. Look out.

204
00:14:01,227 --> 00:14:02,895
Holy Saint Christopher!

205
00:14:03,145 --> 00:14:05,648
Get away from that, she's liquid fire!

206
00:14:07,316 --> 00:14:11,487
Take cover, boys! It ain't popcorn!

207
00:14:21,247 --> 00:14:24,083
Scatter, boys!

208
00:14:25,334 --> 00:14:28,170
God damn it!

209
00:14:31,257 --> 00:14:32,508
Get in, boys!

210
00:14:32,842 --> 00:14:35,261
I'm gonna R-U-N-N-O-F-T!

211
00:14:35,428 --> 00:14:39,181
Come on, boys, come on! Come on!

212
00:14:39,515 --> 00:14:43,602
What are you doing here? You ought
to be in bed, clump snatcher.

213
00:14:43,853 --> 00:14:46,939
You ain't the boss of me!

214
00:14:53,362 --> 00:14:57,033
You candy-butted,
car-thievin' sos-and-sos!

215
00:14:57,366 --> 00:14:59,285
I curse your name!

216
00:14:59,618 --> 00:15:02,371
Go back home and mind your pa!

217
00:15:06,125 --> 00:15:09,629
