That don't do me no good.

220
00:15:17,136 --> 00:15:19,639
Nearest Ford auto man's Bristol.

221
00:15:19,889 --> 00:15:23,225
Hold on. I don't want this pomade,
I want Dapper Dan.

222
00:15:23,476 --> 00:15:26,312
I don't carry Dapper Dan.
I carry Fop.

223
00:15:26,646 --> 00:15:30,066
I don't want Fop, god damn it!
I'm a Dapper Dan man!

224
00:15:30,316 --> 00:15:32,902
Watch your language,
this is a public market.

225
00:15:33,235 --> 00:15:37,573
Now, if you want Dapper Dan,
I can have it in a coupla weeks.

226
00:15:37,823 --> 00:15:41,327
Ain't this a geographical oddity!
Two weeks from everywhere.

227
00:15:41,577 --> 00:15:43,412
Forget it.

228
00:15:43,746 --> 00:15:47,500
Just a dozen hair nets.

229
00:15:47,667 --> 00:15:50,419
Well, didn't look like a one-horse town,

230
00:15:50,586 --> 00:15:53,005
but try finding a decent hair jelly.

231
00:15:53,255 --> 00:15:57,426
- Gopher, Everett?
- No transmission belt for two weeks.

232
00:15:57,593 --> 00:16:00,346
Huh? They dam that river on the 21st.

233
00:16:00,513 --> 00:16:02,932
- Today is the 17th.
- Don't I know it.

234
00:16:03,099 --> 00:16:05,768
We got but four days
to get to that treasure.

235
00:16:06,018 --> 00:16:08,854
After that, it'll be
at the bottom of a lake.

236
00:16:09,105 --> 00:16:10,940
We won't make it walkin'.

237
00:16:11,190 --> 00:16:13,275
- Right...
- Gopher?

238
00:16:13,442 --> 00:16:15,778
But the old tactician's got a plan.

239
00:16:16,028 --> 00:16:19,949
For the transportation,
not keeping my coiffure in order.

240
00:16:20,116 --> 00:16:23,285
How's this a plan?
How we gonna get a car?

241
